const LightTheme = {
    secondaryBackgroundColor: "#F6F9FC",
    mainTextColor: "#111439",
    hoverTextColor: "#11143988",
    quoteTextColor: "#9A9DAE",
    scrollColor1: "#9A9DAE77",
    scrollColor2: "#9A9DAE44",
    dottedLineColor: "linear-gradient(#EBEBEB 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 0%)",
  
    primaryBackgroundColor: "#FFFFFF",
    aboutIdColor: "#CDCDE3",
    pTextColor: "#494B64",
    pBrightColor: "#0E0F20",
  
    viewMoreBtnColor: "#CDCDE3",
    viewMoreBtnHoverColor: "#484B64",
    projectIconColor: "#DADDED",
    projectIconHoverColor: "#484B64",
    constructionTextColor: "#494B6433",
    toolsColor: "#BBBBC9",
  
    copyrightTextColor: "#454A68",
    madeWithTextColor: "#757796ee",

    transition: " 0.0s ease-in-out",
  };
  
  const DarkTheme = {
    secondaryBackgroundColor: "#15161A",
    mainTextColor: "#F6F9FC",
    hoverTextColor: "#F6F9FC88",
    quoteTextColor: "#5F6372",
    scrollColor1: "#5F637277",
    scrollColor2: "#5F637244",
    dottedLineColor: "linear-gradient(#282930 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 0%)",
  
    primaryBackgroundColor: "#121212",
    aboutIdColor: "#2E2F3F",
    pTextColor: "#E4E6F2",
    pBrightColor: "#0E0F20",
  
    viewMoreBtnColor: "#373743",
    viewMoreBtnHoverColor: "#838799",
    projectIconColor: "#373743",
    projectIconHoverColor: "#838799",
    constructionTextColor: "#494B6477",
    toolsColor: "#38394A",
  
    copyrightTextColor: "#65687A",
    madeWithTextColor: "#494B64cc",

    transition: " 0.2s ease",
  };

  const themes = {
      light: LightTheme,
      dark: DarkTheme,
  }

  export default themes;

  //#535566 old made with dark
